high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the side of the desk in the next room.
Pick up the banana from the desk.
Turn and walk out of the room and up to the microwave in the kitchen.
Heat the banana in the microwave then remove it.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the banana into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated banana in the fridge.

high_descs: Put the banana on a plate into the microwave.
Pick up the plate with the fruit from the fridge.
Then put the banana on the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Take the banana and put it on the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight to reach the desk.
Pick the banana from the table.
Go straight to reach the microwave.
Put the banana into the microwave.
Take the banana and turn right to reach the fridge.
Put the banana into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the Banana into the Fridge.
